Name: Senpai Puzzle: Waifu Summer
About the game: Senpai Puzzle: Waifu Summer is a free to play classic sliding puzzle game featuring beautiful Waifus just for you! Classic Sliding Puzzle The classic sliding puzzle with increasing difficulty. FREE Waifus 10 free Waifus in the base game! 3 FREE DLC's 2 FREE DLC image packs and a FREE backgrounds DLC for a total of 51 FREE Waifus! High Quality Waifus All your Waifus are in 4k! Waifu Gallery Easy to use gallery to see your Waifus up close! Chill Music Chill lofi music to enjoy with your Waifus. Technical Settings All the settings you need, including resolution, fullscreen, framerate cap, vsync and more!
